msgstr ""
"Dukungan untuk mengakses pemutar media portabel menggunakan protokol USB "
"Mass Storage"

#: ../plugins/minimode/PLUGININFO:4
msgid "Compact mode for Exaile with a configurable interface"
msgstr "Mode ringkas untuk Exaile dengan antarmuka yang dapat dikonfigurasi"

#: ../plugins/mono/PLUGININFO:3
msgid "Mono"
msgstr "Mono"

#: ../plugins/mono/PLUGININFO:4
msgid "Downmixes audio to one channel."
msgstr "Mencampur audio turun menjadi satu saluran."

#: ../plugins/moodbar/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Show visual representation of the music timeline.\n"
"\n"
"Requires: moodbar"
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan representasi visual dari linimasa musik.\n"
"\n"
"Memerlukan: moodbar"

#: ../plugins/mpris2/PLUGININFO:3
msgid "MPRIS 2"
msgstr "MPRIS 2"

#: ../plugins/mpris2/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Partial support for MPRIS (Media Player Remote Interfacing Specification) "
"2.2, allowing you to control Exaile from supporting clients, for example "
"GNOME Shell"
msgstr ""
"Dukungan parsial untuk MPRIS (Media Player Remote Interfacing Specification) "
"2.2, yang memungkinkan Anda mengendalikan Exaile dari klien yang mendukung, "
"misalnya GNOME Shell"

#: ../plugins/multialarmclock/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Plays music at specific times and days.\n"
"\n"
"Note that when the specified time arrives, Exaile will just act like you "
"pressed the play button, so be sure you have the music you want to hear in "
"your playlist"
msgstr ""
"Memutar musik pada waktu dan hari tertentu.\n"
"\n"
"Perhatikan bahwa saat waktu yang ditentukan tiba, Exaile hanya akan "
"bertindak seperti Anda menekan tombol putar, jadi pastikan Anda memiliki "
"musik yang ingin didengar di daftar putar Anda"

#: ../plugins/musicbrainzcovers/PLUGININFO:3
msgid "MusicBrainz Covers"
msgstr "Sampul MusicBrainz"

#: ../plugins/musicbrainzcovers/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Integrates MusicBrainz for cover search.\n"
"\n"
"Requires: musicbrainzngs"
msgstr ""
"Mengintegrasikan MusicBrainz untuk pencarian sampul.\n"
"\n"
"Memerlukan: musicbrainzngs"

#: ../plugins/notify/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Pops up a notification when playback of a track starts or (optionally) if it "
"is paused/resumed/stopped. Requires libnotify and its typelib file"
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan notifikasi saat pemutaran trek dimulai atau (opsional) jika "
"dijeda/dilanjutkan/dihentikan. Memerlukan libnotify dan berkas typelib-nya"

#: ../plugins/osd/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"A popup window showing information of the currently playing track.\n"
"This plugin is not available on Wayland."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up yang menampilkan informasi trek yang sedang diputar.\n"
"Plugin ini tidak tersedia di Wayland."

#: ../plugins/playlistanalyzer/PLUGININFO:3
msgid "Playlist Analyzer"
msgstr "Penganalisis Daftar Putar"

#: ../plugins/playlistanalyzer/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Tool to help generate HTML5 visualizations of your playlists using d3.js. "
"Optimized for Chrome."
msgstr ""
"Alat untuk membantu membuat visualisasi HTML5 dari daftar putar Anda "
"menggunakan d3.js. Dioptimalkan untuk Chrome."

#: ../plugins/playlistanalyzer/PLUGININFO:5 ../plugins/wikipedia/PLUGININFO:5
msgid "Information"
msgstr "Informasi"

#: ../plugins/podcasts/PLUGININFO:4
msgid "Adds Simple Podcast Support"
msgstr "Menambahkan Dukungan Podcast Sederhana"

#: ../plugins/previewdevice/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Allows playing audio over a secondary device (right click on playlist and "
"select 'preview'). Useful for DJs."
msgstr ""
"Memungkinkan memutar audio melalui perangkat sekunder (klik kanan pada "
"daftar putar lalu pilih 'preview'). Berguna untuk DJ."

#: ../plugins/previewdevice/PLUGININFO:5 ../plugins/streamripper/PLUGININFO:5
msgid "Output"
msgstr "Keluaran"

#: ../plugins/quickbuttons/PLUGININFO:3
msgid "Quick Settings Buttons"
msgstr "Tombol Pengaturan Cepat"

#: ../plugins/quickbuttons/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Provides buttons on bottom of the playlist to quickly change some settings"
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan tombol di bagian bawah daftar putar untuk dengan cepat mengubah "
"beberapa pengaturan"

#: ../plugins/replaygain/PLUGININFO:4
msgid "Enables ReplayGain support"
msgstr "Mengaktifkan dukungan ReplayGain"

#: ../plugins/screensaverpause/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Pauses (and optionally resumes) playback based on screensaver status.\n"
"\n"
"Requires: GNOME, MATE, Cinnamon, XFCE, or KDE Screensaver (does not support "
"XScreenSaver nor XLockMore)"
msgstr ""
"Menjeda (dan secara opsional melanjutkan) pemutaran berdasarkan status "
"screensaver.\n"
"\n"
"Memerlukan: screensaver GNOME, MATE, Cinnamon, XFCE, atau KDE (tidak "
"mendukung XScreenSaver maupun XLockMore)"

#: ../plugins/shutdown/PLUGININFO:4
msgid "Allows for shutdown of the computer at the end of playback."
msgstr "Memungkinkan komputer dimatikan pada akhir pemutaran."

#: ../plugins/somafm/PLUGININFO:3
msgid "SomaFM Radio"
msgstr "Radio SomaFM"

#: ../plugins/somafm/PLUGININFO:4
#, python-format
msgid "SomaFM Radio list%s%s"
msgstr "Daftar Radio SomaFM%s%s"

#: ../plugins/streamripper/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Allows you to record streams with streamripper.\n"
"Depends: streamripper"
msgstr ""
"Memungkinkan Anda merekam stream dengan streamripper.\n"
"Bergantung pada: streamripper"

#: ../plugins/wikipedia/PLUGININFO:4
msgid ""
"Provides Wikipedia information about the current artist.\n"
"\n"
"Requires: webkit2gtk and its typelib file"
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan informasi Wikipedia tentang artis saat ini.\n"
"\n"
"Memerlukan: webkit2gtk dan berkas typelib-nya"

#: ../plugins/winmmkeys/PLUGININFO:2
msgid "Multimedia keys for Windows"
msgstr "Tombol multimedia untuk Windows"

#: ../plugins/winmmkeys/PLUGININFO:4
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Adds support for keyboard multimedia keys on Windows.\n"
"\n"
"Requires: pynput (%s) (included in the Exaile installer)\n"
"\n"
"Warning: When this plugin is enabled, Exaile will process every key event in "
"the Windows session, which may cause some security software to detect Exaile "
"as a keylogger."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan dukungan untuk tombol multimedia keyboard di Windows.\n"
"\n"
"Memerlukan: pynput (%s) (disertakan dalam penginstal Exaile)\n"
"\n"
"Peringatan: Saat plugin ini diaktifkan, Exaile akan memproses setiap "
"kejadian tombol dalam sesi Windows, yang dapat menyebabkan beberapa "
"perangkat lunak keamanan mendeteksi Exaile sebagai keylogger."

#: ../data/exaile.desktop.in:4 ../data/exaile.appdata.xml.in:6
msgid "Exaile"
msgstr "Exaile"

#: ../data/exaile.desktop.in:5
msgid "Music Player"
msgstr "Pemutar Musik"

#: ../data/exaile.desktop.in:7 ../data/exaile.appdata.xml.in:7
msgid "Listen to, explore, or manage your audio collection"
msgstr "Dengarkan, jelajahi, atau kelola koleksi audio Anda"

#: ../data/exaile.desktop.in:13
msgid "Music;Player;Library;Collection;MP3;OGG;FLAC;MP4"
msgstr "Musik;Pemutar;Pustaka;Koleksi;MP3;OGG;FLAC;MP4"

#: ../data/exaile.appdata.xml.in:9
msgid ""
"Exaile is a music player with a simple interface and powerful music "
"management capabilities. Features include automatic fetching of album art, "
"lyrics fetching, streaming internet radio, tabbed playlists, smart playlists "
"with extensive filtering/search capabilities, and much more."
msgstr ""
"Exaile adalah pemutar musik dengan antarmuka sederhana dan kemampuan "
"pengelolaan musik yang kuat. Fitur-fiturnya mencakup pengambilan sampul "
"album secara otomatis, pengambilan lirik, streaming radio internet, daftar "
"putar bertab, daftar putar cerdas dengan kemampuan penyaringan/pencarian "
"yang luas, dan banyak lagi."

#: ../data/exaile.appdata.xml.in:15
msgid ""
"Exaile is written using python and GTK+ and is easily extensible via "
"plugins. There are over 50 plugins distributed with Exaile that include "
"advanced track tagging, last.fm scrobbling, support for portable media "
"players, podcasts, internet radio such as icecast and Soma.FM, ReplayGain, "
"output via a secondary output device (great for DJs!), and much more."
msgstr ""
"Exaile ditulis menggunakan Python dan GTK+ serta mudah diperluas melalui "
"plugin. Ada lebih dari 50 plugin yang didistribusikan bersama Exaile, yang "
"mencakup penandaan trek tingkat lanjut, scrobbling last.fm, dukungan untuk "
"pemutar media portabel, podcast, radio internet seperti Icecast dan Soma.FM, "
"ReplayGain, keluaran melalui perangkat keluaran sekunder (sangat cocok untuk "
"DJ!), dan banyak lagi."

